'''边境㹴'''（{{lang-en|Border Terrier}}）是一种来自英国的㹴犬，体型细小，成犬身高（至肩膊）28-41厘米，重5.2-7.0公斤，與{{link-en|丹迪丁蒙㹴|Dandie Dinmont Terrier}}<ref name="Oberlin">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oberlin.edu/faculty/scarrier/Border_Terrier/Border_History.html |title=History of the Border Terrier |accessdate=2014-07-23 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723062738/http://www.oberlin.edu/faculty/scarrier/Border_Terrier/Border_History.html |archivedate=2014-07-23}}</ref>和{{link-en|貝林登㹴|Bedlington Terrier}}<ref name="Oberlin"/>有共同祖先。

